messages.message:
*Masters of UDF*

1. Is there an example of a UDF which writes an arbitrary file to disk?
2. Is there a useful collection of common UDF situations that I can roll into a set of UDF recipes?
1. There’s some documentation on it here, is that what you’re referring to? https://www.instabase.com/docs/content/apps/flow/add-steps-to-flow/options/apply-udf.html?highlight=apply%20udf%20options
2. What do you mean by a UDF recipe? Had started creating a lib here, but the UDFs here are very old https://github.com/instabase/customer-solutions/tree/master/flow-component-lib/apply_udf_functions
@Balaram or @Kerry might have a good way they’re versioning/recording UDFs right now too (also feel free to add your UDFs to the customer-solutions repo!)
